{"tid":503493,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(扮工+放灰)小弟今日生日, 想向各巴打絲打乞句生日快樂,身體健康","createTime":"2017-12-19T02:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T02:07:39.000Z","uid":150427,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a429ab5907426b0dd99f0466a7a41c7b6d5bff20","tid":503493,"uid":150427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 昨晚腸胃痛,  痛到嘔左成晚沒咩點上床, 今日又要頂住返工)<br />\n<br />\n唔...可唔可以俾我先放下小小灰? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日開始就31歲了, 又係一事沒成, 日日返工放工返份牛工。<br />\n其實對我黎講上年真係唔多好, 除左家人身體之外, 自己身體都唔知出左咩事(可以睇返我舊post), 自己呢年出出入入醫院, 使左成幾萬蚊都沒咩用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  而原本plan 好左想去讀書進修都做唔到, 好多事都不如人願咁。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知係唔係人老左, 睇野開始睇化左(變左廢老??<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ), 少左熱情passion, 多左無奈同忍受。<br />\n<br />\n細個成日覺得自己係好叻好特別, 將來會上位同有突出表現; 但呢幾年D經歷(社會, 個人, 父母等等)令我個人同心拉返出黎現實。老實講我而家真係只求平平淡淡, 大家平平安安、身體健康, 已經好滿足。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打完上邊D灰野, 又要繼續扮工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我都係想向各位乞句 &quot;生日快樂,身體健康&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 同埋留小小言俾我, 等我可以取下暖自我安慰<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613133c9204dc85145d47aa2486e71161bc2f08d","tid":503493,"uid":69177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:15:25.000Z","msg":"祝你生日快樂，身體健康<br />\n事事順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbca016ec176dbe19a8ad0dd311c2945a18e16d","tid":503493,"uid":153927,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T02:26:17.000Z"